Sentencas: We demonstrate a cup-shaped yttria-doped barium zirconate (BYZ) membrane array fuel cell fabricated by silicon micromachining processes.
Titulo: Cup-shaped yttria-doped barium zirconate membrane fuel cell array

Sentencas: The surface area of the BYZ membrane was increased by making the nano thin film BYZ from flat membrane to a three-dimensional membrane.
Titulo: Cup-shaped yttria-doped barium zirconate membrane fuel cell array

Sentencas: A BYZ thin film electrolyte with a thickness of 300 nm was deposited on pre-patterned silicon substrate with cup-shaped trenches.
Titulo: Cup-shaped yttria-doped barium zirconate membrane fuel cell array

Sentencas: The fuel cell voltage-current curve was measured at 400 degrees C to verify the functionality of the geometric increase of electricity from the three-dimensional membrane electrolyte.
Titulo: Cup-shaped yttria-doped barium zirconate membrane fuel cell array
